      "seed": 2003, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 2004, "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null, "updated": 1774700000000, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "Platform.h  —  namespace aether::ipc::platform\n\nserverSocket(name)    acceptClient(fd)      connectToServer(name)    closeFd(fd)\ncreateSharedMemory(size)    sendFd(sock, fd, data)    recvFd(sock, &fd, buf)\nsendSignal(fd)    recvSignal(fd)    shutdownConnection(fd)    getPeerUid(fd)",
      "originalText": "Platform.h  —  namespace aether::ipc::platform\n\nserverSocket(name)    acceptClient(fd)      connectToServer(name)    closeFd(fd)\ncreateSharedMemory(size)    sendFd(sock, fd, data)    recvFd(sock, &fd, buf)\nsendSignal(fd)    recvSignal(fd)    shutdownConnection(fd)    getPeerUid(fd)",
      "autoResize": true, "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle", "containerId": "api_box", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

